(1722, 3, '2019-01-23 22:12:29', '2019-01-23 22:12:29', '<p><h3><b><font color=#0A65BA face=\"Comic Sans MS,arial,verdana\" >FORMULARIO DE CONTACTO</font></h3></b> </p>\r\n<br  />\r\n\r\n<p><font size=4 color=#2D98D5 face=\"Comic Sans MS,arial,verdana\">Nombre</font>\r\n    [text* your-name] </p>\r\n<br  />\r\n\r\n<p><font size=4 color=#2D98D5 face=\"Comic Sans MS,arial,verdana\">Celular\r\n</font>[tel* Celular] </p>\r\n<br  />\r\n\r\n<p><font size=4 color=#2D98D5 face=\"Comic Sans MS,arial,verdana\">Email</font>\r\n    [email* your-email] </p>\r\n<br  />\r\n\r\n<p><font size=4 color=#2D98D5 face=\"Comic Sans MS,arial,verdana\">Empresa</font>\r\n    [text* your-company] </p>\r\n<br  />\r\n\r\n<p><font size=4 color=#2D98D5 face=\"Comic Sans MS,arial,verdana\">RUC</font> \r\n[tel RUC]</p>\r\n<br  />\r\n\r\n[submit \"Enviar\"]\n1\nPlata Perú \"[your-subject]\"\nPlata Perú <wordpress@miplata.com.pe>\nalsanchez@tebca.com.pe\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\n\r\nInformación: \r\n\r\nNombre: [your-name]\r\nEmpresa:[your-company]\r\nCorreo:  [your-email]\r\nCelular: [Celular]\r\nRUC: [RUC]\r\n\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on Plata Perú (https://stplatape.wpenginepowered.com)\nReply-To: [your-email]\n\n\n\n\nPlata Perú \"[your-subject]\"\nPlata Perú <wordpress@miplata.com.pe>\n[your-email]\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on Plata Perú (https://stplatape.wpenginepowered.com)\nReply-To: servicios@tebca.com.pe\n\n\n\nGracias, tu mensaje fue enviado con éxito\nHubo un error. Por favor, intente de nuevo.\nPor favor, agregar tu número de celular para contactar contigo más rápido.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nYou must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\nThe field is required.\nThe field is too long.\nThe field is too short.\nThere was an unknown error uploading the file.\nYou are not allowed to upload files of this type.\nThe file is too big.\nThere was an error uploading the file.\nThe date format is incorrect.\nThe date is before the earliest one allowed.\nThe date is after the latest one allowed.\nThe number format is invalid.\nThe number is smaller than the minimum allowed.\nThe number is larger than the maximum allowed.\nThe answer to the quiz is incorrect.\nThe e-mail address entered is invalid.\nThe URL is invalid.\nThe telephone number is invalid.', 'Contact form 1', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'contact-form-1', '', '', '2023-09-27 10:05:36', '2023-09-27 15:05:36', '', 0, 'https://platape.wpengine.com/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=1722', 0, 'wpcf7_contact_form', '', 0),
